3.	Build a personal Portfolio website 

Aim: To Build a Personal Portfolio website.

Alogrithm:

Step1: Start the process and Set up a html file.
Step2: In the <head> section include the meta, title and style tags.
Step3: Create the components and write the code for the website title, description, navigation menu and content for each section.
Step4: Write the CSS code in the style tag.
Step5: Run the file in browser to display the output.
Step6: Stop the process


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>My Portfolio</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    header { background: #04aab6; color: #fff; padding: 20px; text-align: center; }
    nav a { color: #fff; margin: 0 10px; text-decoration: none; }
    section { padding: 40px; max-width: 800px; margin: auto; }
    h2 { color: #333; }
    .skills, .projects { display: flex; gap: 20px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .card { border: 1px solid #ccc; padding: 20px; flex: 1; min-width: 200px; }
    footer { background: #04aab6; color: #fff; text-align: center; padding: 10px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <h1>KASC</h1>
    <p>CTIT Student | Web Developer</p>
    <nav>
      <a href="#about">About</a>
      <a href="#skills">Skills</a>
      <a href="#projects">Projects</a>
      <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <section id="about">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>Hello! I'm a BSc IT student passionate about coding, design, and building cool projects.</p>
  </section>

  <section id="skills">
    <h2>Skills</h2>
    <div class="skills">
      <div class="card">HTML & CSS</div>
      <div class="card">JavaScript</div>
      <div class="card">Python</div>
      <div class="card">React (basic)</div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="projects">
    <h2>Projects</h2>
    <div class="projects">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Quiz App</h3>
        <p>A simple quiz app built with JavaScript.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Portfolio Website</h3>
        <p>This very site showcasing my skills and projects.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section id="contact">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Email: 23ucit075@kasc.ac.in</p>
    <p>LinkedIn: linkedin.com/in/kasc_ctit</p>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2025 CTITian. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>


